# MotoApp Project Context

- Use `docs/project-map.md` as the default architecture map before planning feature changes.
- Keep fuel domain logic in `src/state/fuel.tsx` (or dedicated domain helpers), not in page-level UI components.
- Keep persistence logic in `src/lib/storage.ts` or nearby storage service files.
- For each new feature, start from a short brief:
  - Goal
  - Constraints
  - UX flow
  - Touched files
  - Acceptance criteria
  - Out of scope
- For substantial edits, validate with `npm run lint` and `npm run test`.

